{"tid":2284370,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"驚！台大五天內3人輕生　20歲男在社科院墜下　全身骨折命危","createTime":"2020-11-13T08:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T15:08:13.000Z","uid":209657,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"22891d522bf04e27659f3e40e3061af4d4a8628c","tid":2284370,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"台灣大學校園又發生墜樓！今天下午近3時許，台大學生聽見社會科學院圖書館外有墜落撞擊聲，經過查看發現，一名年約20歲的男子疑似從高處墜下，跌落大樓的水池旁，校方緊急報案通知救護車到場，發現墜樓男子意識不清、全身肢體多處骨折，緊急將他送往台大醫院急救。由於今天<span class=\"red\">正值台大期中考週</span>，不少學生在圖書館內溫習功課，目睹墜樓過程後受到極大驚嚇。<br />\n<br />\n台大這星期發生數起學生事故，先是9日1名女大生墜樓送醫不治，11日大陸籍學生在宿舍上吊輕生，今天又有男學生墜樓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/QbheZVZlRHp3XecxswLxgmPEfxY=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D6VEBOPNCVCMDAP4ZLCJQ7VEWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQbheZVZlRHp3XecxswLxgmPEfxY%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD6VEBOPNCVCMDAP4ZLCJQ7VEWE.jpg&h=8c094e11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a93eae20b74add177927dd75c790abb2ce5a8eae","tid":2284370,"uid":283761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c24ced7a80a6655eb26b94a0c5132a65b63ce5","tid":2284370,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201113/QQJDGVPAZNCUVATPVAYDFK5E4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FQQJDGVPAZNCUVATPVAYDFK5E4Q%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=54f0241f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FQQJDGVPAZNCUVATPVAYDFK5E4Q%2F&h=13b9b6b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201113/QQJDGVPAZNCUVATPVAYDFK5E4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"b3519e2eb9a7437e02d706489123f3fbe4996257","tid":2284370,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:57:13.000Z","msg":"台仔開始驚武統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55081c9e29b650011d0eb6f1bad1ec21166adc88","tid":2284370,"uid":20317,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f17f3967e055ec142eaaf133ece537b28480018","tid":2284370,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1081bb7d9cfe753a6489dc8decfa8dcedab7eaf8","tid":2284370,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"1名男學生疑從社科院大樓墜落，<span class=\"red\">摔在圖書館落地窗前方水池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>，其他學生見狀立刻報案"},{"pid":"74fa8d0c789ed5341455981411954cc4faae835c","tid":2284370,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:02:20.000Z","msg":"事發下午台大校長校長管中閔剛好發信給全校師生，對於未能及時避免前2樁憾事感到痛心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/13/2879916-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F13%2F2879916-PH.jpg&h=0dade3aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19a2b798b4a63d83a02441308765d7eafc1cface","tid":2284370,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:05:00.000Z","msg":"科大跳蘑菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5814c6c6558582ed16996d3238dc55f54d9b210","tid":2284370,"uid":20317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:11:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce2343cc07954697cec9613719f89c4d0a9d59dd","tid":2284370,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT